jade.webservice.dynamicClient
Class DynamicClientProperties

java.lang.Object
  jade.webservice.dynamicClient.DynamicClientProperties

public class DynamicClientProperties
extends java.lang.Object

Configuration class of a DynamicClient. For details see the WSDC user guide.

The default values are:

  • noWrap: false
  • safeMode: true
  • packageName: -
  • classPath: -
  • tmpDir: system property java.io.tmpdir
